    </h1>
    <p>
      Thank you for setting up your password at Analytica. To ensure the security of your 
      account, we kindly ask you to confirm your password by clicking on the button below:
    </p>

    <p>
      For security reasons, this link is only valid for the next 48 hours.
    </p>

    <a href="<%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
