      our support team at support@analytica.com.
    </p>

  </div>
  <div>
    <p style="font-style: italic; font-size: 14px;">
      In case the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the following URL into your browser:
    </p>
    <p style="font-style: oblique; font-size: 12px; color: #2682df; text-decoration: none;" href="<%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>">
      <%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>
